The piano cover song of Studio Ghibli especially. I mean, I'm not the one to judged. The original version of the songs are good. But your cover version is so out of this world and healing my soul. If I have insomnia, troubled at night and feel empty, I would heard your cover. Especially you put so many soothing nature sounds. There are so many variety. From the gentle one, the angst one, even the gentle happy one. I feel soft and touched! My favorite is One Summer Night / Inochi no Namae piano cover in night with moon, grass field, and the sound of insect's vibration (what's the name again). As if heaven's sing comes down from the sky and greet the people! 

May I ask for a request? I love and trust all of your piano cover (either it is Studio Ghibli or Disney), but may I ask the cover's bgm? I mean, would you put a single wind chimes sound for BGM, please? 

Either way, I thanked you because you covered Disney, and especially Studio Ghibli songs. I appreciate your hard works and gentle sense of art to put all in these videos together. I can't thank you enough for the beautiful covers, beautiful images, and nature sound BGM. Thank you. Please keep going on!
